Further information
Successful Candidate must have a minimum of 1 year experience in a similar position in a 5/4 start hotel and can communicate fluent in English and Arabic.
The associate will be in charge of Opera & handling guest complaining, has exceptional interpersonal skills and shows commitment. Is able to work under stress and can handle it, drives for results and has a concern for quality.
Successful candidate must demonstrate the following competencies:
Responses to guest requests
Shows commitment for quality
Takes personal responsibility
Drives for results
Completes assigned tasks on time
